casebody.data:
Salvatore J. MORETTI, Petitioner
v.
BERGEN COUNTY PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE No. 19-5284 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019 Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of New Jersey, Appellate Division dismissed. See Rule 39.8. Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
